Inspect the receipt chain head or verify an envelope (GaussClaw extension)

Usage: receipt <COMMAND>

Commands:
  head    Print the current receipt-chain head and its TSA-anchor proof
  verify  Verify a Cryptographic Trajectory Envelope file
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
